---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Cookie Policy | Senkai World"
  description="Learn how Senkai World uses cookies to improve your browsing experience."
>

<section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 py-16">
  <h1 class="mb-8 text-4xl font-extrabold text-white">
    Cookie Policy
  </h1>

  <p class="mb-8 text-sm text-slate-400">
    Last Updated: July 2026
  </p>

  <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none prose-headings:text-white prose-p:text-slate-300 prose-li:text-slate-300">

    <p>
      Senkai World uses cookies and similar technologies to improve your
      browsing experience, analyze website traffic, and provide a secure and
      reliable service.
    </p>

    <h2>Cookies We Use</h2>

    <h3>Essential Cookies</h3>

    <p>
      These cookies are necessary for the website to function properly and
      cannot be disabled.
    </p>

    <h3>Analytics Cookies</h3>

    <p>
      We use Google Analytics to understand how visitors use our website, such
      as which pages are viewed and how users interact with our content. This
      helps us improve the overall experience.
    </p>

    <h3>Security Cookies</h3>

    <p>
      Cloudflare may use cookies to enhance website security, improve
      performance, and protect against malicious traffic.
    </p>

    <h2>Managing Cookies</h2>

    <p>
      Most web browsers allow you to control or disable cookies through their
      settings. Please note that disabling certain cookies may affect some
      website functionality.
    </p>

    <p>
      By continuing to use Senkai World, you consent to the use of cookies as
      described in this policy.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>

    <p>
      If you have any questions about this Cookie Policy, please contact us at:
    </p>

    <p>
      <strong>senkaiworld.in@gmail.com</strong>
    </p>

  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>